            <!-- Section 6: Conclusion -->
            <section class="mt-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-700 mb-4">Conclusion</h2>
                <p>
                    Java has stood the test of time because it evolves while staying true to its core principles. Its relevance spans from mobile app development to enterprise systems and cloud computing. For students and professionals alike, mastering Java means building skills that transfer easily to other programming languages and platforms.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4">
                    Whether you’re developing Android apps, building large-scale backend systems, or experimenting with AI-powered projects, Java gives you the stability, scalability, and security you need to succeed.
                </p>
            </section>

